Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:31.06,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:39.64,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Let's break the tight-fisted night!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:45.18,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,We have no interest in treasure chests
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:48.65,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,A pocket of romance, and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:01:58.59,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:04.64,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Let's pile up all the dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:10.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,And go find the thing we're looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:14.31,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,A pocket of coins, and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:24.65,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,We are!
